If you’re seeing this, thank you for being part of my journey even if I have not been as present online. This year has been very freeing for me to let go of the expectations of posting regularly, coming up with just the right thing to say, judging the amount of interaction and likes per post, keeping up with the trends, or comparing myself to what seems like an endless amount of perfect people with perfect lives. I’m spending more time being present with the people around me, being kinder to myself for growing older, and practicing letting go of envy. I’m so grateful to you all. May your 2024 be wildly better than any of your expectations. With much love, Alisa 🤍
